  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Standing Counsel for the Comptroller General of patents, designs and trade marks
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    The Attorney General is recruiting to fill an existing vacancy providing the Comptroller with advice and to act on his behalf before the Courts.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="column-two-thirds metadata-column">
